OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FThe new Welsh health minister has said
OL,7,Feradicating two-year waits for NHS
OL,8,Ftreatment could take up to four years
OL,9,F- after the new First Minister
OL,10,Fpreviously said it should happen
OL,11,F"within months".
OL,13,FDuring his first official visit, Mabon
OL,14,Fap Gwynfor told ITV Cymru Wales at
OL,15,FNeath Port Talbot Hospital that he
OL,16,Fwill make sure two-year waits "are
OL,17,Feliminated by the end of our term".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
