CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FBut speaking on ITV Cymru Wales' The
OL,7,FInterviews programme, just weeks
OL,8,Fbefore the election, Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fleader and now First Minister Rhun ap
OL,10,FIorwerth said he expected "to be able
OL,11,Fto get rid of those longest waiting
OL,12,Ftimes within a matter of months".
OL,14,FHe had criticised the previous
OL,15,FGovernment's efforts, under Welsh
OL,16,FLabour, to eradicate two-year waits,
OL,17,Fsomething it promised but failed to do
OL,18,Fduring their term.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
