PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FWhen pushed on Plaid Cymru's original
OL,7,Fpledge, the health minister said:
OL,8,F"Yeah that's the aim of what we're
OL,9,Fhoping to achieve, now if we can do
OL,10,Fthat quicker - absolutely. We will be
OL,11,Fpushing this at pace, making sure that
OL,12,Fwe work with the NHS in Wales, with
OL,13,Fthe health boards, to ensure that
OL,14,Fthose numbers come down as soon as we
OL,15,Fcan."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
