CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FReform UK Wales' shadow health
OL,7,Fminister James Evans described the
OL,8,Fhealth minister's comments today as a
OL,9,F"U-turn" and called on the First
OL,10,FMinister to clarify when the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment will get the longest waits
OL,12,Fdown.
OL,14,F"That is not acceptable. If they are
OL,15,Fnot going to get this down as
OL,16,Fpromised, then they need to explain
OL,17,Fthat and why to the people of Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,F"This seems to be a u-turn on some of
OL,7,Ftheir policies already between what
OL,8,Fthe First Minister was saying during
OL,9,Fthe election campaign and now what his
OL,10,Fcabinet secretary for health is
OL,11,Fsaying, so I think they all need to
OL,12,Fstart singing off the same hymn sheet."
OL,14,FResponding to Reform UK, the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment maintained the First
OL,16,FMinister's pledge on clearing waiting
OL,17,Ftimes within months was accurate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
