OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FFigures published on Thursday revealed
OL,7,Fthat in March almost 2,600 patient
OL,8,Fpathways were still waiting longer
OL,9,Fthan 24 months.
OL,11,FAround 529,100 individual patients
OL,12,Fwere waiting for NHS treatment
OL,13,Foverall, but that number has fallen
OL,14,Ffor 10 consecutive months.
OL,16,FWelsh Labour said that the fall is "a
OL,17,Fresult of the hard work of NHS staff
OL,18,Fand the previous Welsh Labour
OL,19,FGovernment's #120 million investment
OL,20,Fin cutting waiting lists".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
