FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779387068
OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FIts interim leader and health
OL,7,Fspokesperson Ken Skates added: "There
OL,8,Fis more work to be done, and it's now
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru's responsibility to ensure
OL,10,Fthis progress does not falter.
OL,12,F"Continuing to ensure more people are
OL,13,Fseen more quickly will mean taking
OL,14,Fdecisive action, not just
OL,15,Fcommissioning reviews and plans."
OL,17,FJohn McKnight, from Gorseinon, has
OL,18,Fbeen waiting more than three years for
OL,19,Fa hip operation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
