OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FThe 78-year-old widower recently had
OL,7,Fto return home early from his holiday
OL,8,Fin Turkey because he was in so much
OL,9,Fpain.
OL,11,F"I'm getting on in age and it's slowly
OL,12,Fwearing me down. It's having an effect
OL,13,Fon my health, I'm falling over all the
OL,14,Ftime," he said.
OL,16,F"I want to make the most of the time
OL,17,FI've got left. I used to enjoy fishing
OL,18,For going down to see the Swans, but
OL,19,Fthat's out of the question right now.
OL,20,FIt's ruining my life slowly."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
