OL,3,CWelsh Government accused of U-turn on
OL,4,Cwaiting lists pledge
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has committed in
OL,7,Fits first 100 days to commissioning an
OL,8,Findependent review of NHS performance
OL,9,Fin Wales, with a particular focus on
OL,10,Fthe impact of waiting lists on
OL,11,Fpopulation health.
OL,13,FA new expert task group will also be
OL,14,Fset up to develop plans for up to ten
OL,15,Fnew elective care hubs across Wales,
OL,16,Fwith a 'delivery plan' due to be
OL,17,Fpublished by the end of 2026.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
